284
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,519
[SPEAKER_02] To je sve već obojano, zar ne?

285
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,240
[SPEAKER_02] Da, baš tako.

286
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ovo je samo zabavna priča.

287
00:19:54,319 --> 00:19:57,119
[SPEAKER_02] Tako sam jako uzbuđen zbog tog izazova.

288
00:19:57,200 --> 00:20:03,839
