367
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] To je na engleskom.

368
00:25:34,559 --> 00:25:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] U redu.

369
00:25:35,039 --> 00:25:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da koristimo dobar predložak.

370
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,519
