371
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:39,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam poput, eh, vjerojatno je bezazopasno.

372
00:25:39,599 --> 00:25:40,720
[SPEAKER_01] To će nas ubiti.

373
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,240
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, to ima svoje granice, naravno.

374
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:46,079
